Package ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.compiler

Class BinaryOperation

java.lang.Object
ca.on.oicr.gsi.shesmu.compiler.BinaryOperation
public abstract class BinaryOperation extends Object
Describes how to perform an binary operation

The operation must be able to take exactly two arguments and know what to do based only on the types of the operands.
